{"tid":2507394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前註冊處長：限查冊助長舞弊","createTime":"2021-04-28T03:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T03:43:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3435e6e91bb6159505a167459eb33ebd1a866c20","tid":2507394,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/PINJPBNWAFEGJFMUEPDJ2UWHFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FPINJPBNWAFEGJFMUEPDJ2UWHFQ%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0vo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=2b80fdf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FPINJPBNWAFEGJFMUEPDJ2UWHFQ%2F&h=34098de2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/PINJPBNWAFEGJFMUEPDJ2UWHFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n前註冊處長：限查冊助長舞弊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hcOeTRIo3GtUQMWMZERrE3t_74E=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ROI27ARCVVAIDL5MWZDM54QNHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhcOeTRIo3GtUQMWMZERrE3t_74E%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FROI27ARCVVAIDL5MWZDM54QNHY.jpg&h=6a394cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾悟思<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】繼車牌查冊後，政府欲進一步封殺公司查冊，早前建議限制公眾查閱公司董事身份證及通常住址。公司註冊處前處長鍾悟思昨在《明報》撰文，質疑新規定將令企業腐敗，增加舞弊行為，形容傳媒進行調查報道時不受阻礙地查冊的能力，是香港透明度和公民自由的根本重要基石。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂損國際金融中心聲譽<br />\n<br />\n鍾悟思早在2013年已力批政府欲收緊公司查冊，近日再度撰文，表示大批需要對董事進行定期查冊的專業人士將大幅受阻，令企業腐敗，增加欺詐和洗錢等舞弊行為的潛在機率。他特別提到許多新聞界成員需定期進行公司查冊，進行調查報道時不受阻礙地查冊的能力，是香港透明度和公民自由的根本重要基石。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前指相關建議有參考英國等地，鍾悟思回應指英國有要求所有公司必須提交經過審計的賬目，香港未有相關要求，還允許董事隱藏居住地址和身份證號碼，問題將變本加厲。<br />\n<br />\n鍾悟思續指，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，儘管保護個人私隱和防止濫用查冊資料很重要，但保持不受限制的公眾查冊權利，來確保充份的公司資訊披露和透明性也至關重要，為保障債權人、投資者等公眾利益，董事放棄一定程度的個人私隱在所難免。<br />\n<br />\n如實施新規定，他認為將削弱作為香港商業生活核心的問責、全面披露和透明性的原則，對香港國際金融中心的形象和聲譽產生不利影響，建議政府重新考慮是否推行這些具潛在危害的提案。<br />\n<br />\n鍾悟思1973年於英國牛津大學畢業，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"66ca24e991d2e0812ec3c0a4ace07b2000465be5","tid":2507394,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"考第一係唔會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d167fbff8950cc6c2667cbdb882ca3a5571946","tid":2507394,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"仲想用香港公司同北韓伊朗交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加美國調查成本"},{"pid":"14ab5d8ff92b5a40f41da44b5af14c98ca91b23e","tid":2507394,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d167fbff8950cc6c2667cbdb882ca3a5571946","tid":2507394,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"仲想用香港公司同北韓伊朗交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加美國調查成本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"美國有籍口制裁香港"},{"pid":"84b355f143fef27a31e96c23d832ac50cb0e72c1","tid":2507394,"uid":308618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ca24e991d2e0812ec3c0a4ace07b2000465be5","tid":2507394,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"考第一係唔會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:33:09.000Z","msg":"我睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我未聽過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔清楚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲係你嘅觀點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大聲唔代表啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有大家講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我未聽過佢種講法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" cl